B
A^c
P(B|A^c)=\frac{1}{9}
\begin{eqnarray} P(B)&=&P(B|A)\cdot P(A)+P(B|A^c)\cdot P(A^c)\\ &=&P(B|A)\cdot P(A)+P(B|A^c)\cdot(1- P(A)) \end{eqnarray} 
P(B)=0\cdot \frac{1}{10} + \frac{1}{9}\cdot\left(1-\frac{1}{10}\right)=\frac{1}{10}
